1f441-fe0f-200d-1f5e8-fe0f.title: Eye in Speech Bubble
aliases: I Am A Witness
I Am a Witness
1f441-fe0f-200d-1f5e8-fe0f.description: A speech bubble showing an eye inside. When using text-to-speech on Apple platforms, this emoji is read aloud as: "Eye in speech bubble representing anti-bullying campaign". This emoji was released in conjunction with the Ad Council for the I Am A Witness campaign. The Eye in Speech Bubble emoji is a sequence of the 👁 Eye and 🗨 Left Speech Bubble emojis. These are combined using a zero width joiner between each character and display as a single emoji on supported platforms. Eye in Speech Bubble was added to Emoji 2.0 in 2015.

1f5e8-fe0f.title: Left Speech Bubble
1f5e8-fe0f.description: A left-facing speech bubble, which was included in Unicode 7.0, but not considered a standard addition for the purposes of emoji presentation. Left Speech Bubble was approved as part of Unicode 7.0 in 2014 and added to Emoji 2.0 in 2015.
